title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: When attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export operation should complete successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Insert a table inside a grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data from the table.
